Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}終わりが来たら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}なんて言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}どうせなら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}哀しくない様に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:13.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}いつかのあなたの言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}酷く刺さってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:22.42,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}温かく残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}知れば知るだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.40,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}何かを求めてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.64,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}どこにも行かないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}どこにも行けないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:45.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}忘れないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:51.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}何故か遠くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:57.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}瞳の裏にいつも君は居る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:02.12,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}今も　ずっとそう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.13,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}いつかね　もう少しね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:09.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}世界に優しい風が吹いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}何か変わるのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}「帰りたい場所がある」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}誰もがこの星の子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}約束はね　大事にね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.98,OP_JP,,0,0,5,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}温かく残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}如果抵达终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}该说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}索性就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}别显得太难过就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:13.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}你从前说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}仍深深刺痛着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:22.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}却残留些许温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}明明不必深究就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.40,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}却不由得去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}我不会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}也无法离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:45.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}明明从未忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:51.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}为何渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:57.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}你始终存在于我眼眸深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:02.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}现在也是 永远都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.13,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}总有一天 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:09.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}当世间微风轻拂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}是否会带来什么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}「有想要回去的地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}我们都是这世界的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,360)}要好好珍惜约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(360,0)}那份温暖仍残留心间
